nt\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService/GetCart操作异常时段耗时从正常的2.3-8.7ms增加到7-31ms，延迟倍数3.6-7.1倍；AddItem操作从3.8-5.2ms增加到18.5-20.3ms，延迟倍数4-5倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShippingService操作异常时段延迟显著增加，GetQuote从203-216ms增加到500-1526ms，延迟倍数2.5-7倍；ShipOrder从225ms增加到873ms，延迟倍数3.9倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**根因定位**: `checkoutservice` 是主要的性能瓶颈，其 `PlaceOrder` 操作在异常时段响应时间翻倍，这影响了整个下单流程。\n\n**关键发现**:\n1. **checkoutservice** 的延迟传播到其下游服务（cartservice、shippingservice、emailservice）\n2. **cartservice** 的延迟问题最为严重，多个操作延迟倍数达到4-7倍\n3. **shippingservice** 也出现显著延迟，特别是 GetQuote 操作\n\n**影响路径**: frontend → checkoutservice → [cartservice, shippingservice, emailservice] 的调用链都受到显著影响，其中 checkoutservice 是根因，其他服务是受害者。\n\n**建议**: 需要重点检查 checkoutservice 的资源使用情况、数据库连接池配置以及 cartservice 的性能表现。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "cc3b1830-139", "component": "adservice-2", "reason": "AdService--gc rule executed 179 times causing GCHelper memory pressure and node_memory_usage_rate increase", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(adservice-2)", "observation": "Found AdService--gc-1749359425 rule executed 179 times, Agent failed to start and GCHelper triggered"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(aiops-k8s-08)", "observation": "node_memory_usage_rate increased from 60.72% to 65.14%, node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased 12.49%"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(cc3b1830-139)", "observation": "cartservice-2